snippet: A day after prosecutors raided its headquarters in a tax-evasion investigation, Deutsche Bank disclosed that earnings would be weak, but called it "guidance" rather than a "profit warning."
abstract: A day after prosecutors raided its headquarters in a tax-evasion investigation, Deutsche Bank disclosed that earnings would be weak, but called it "guidance" rather than a "profit warning."

headline.main: Deutsche Bank Says Earnings Will Be Weak
headline.print_headline: After Raid, A Warning Of a Drag On Profit
